Dialogs.Dialog: Let me ask you something, you turned it off without saving it, didn't you? Why?
Hey. Didn't you turn it off without saving it? Huh.
Hey you didn't save it, you turned it off. Already.
You know what, you turned it off without saving it, didn't you? Do you want to piss me off?
He didn't save it again, he turned it off! Why? I'm really disappointed.
There you go again, turning it off without saving it. Rinko definitely does not like that.
Once again, you turned it off without saving it. Do you want people to hate you? I can't allow it anymore.
Oh my God how many times have I told you not to turn it off without saving it? I won't forgive you anymore, so be prepared.
You know how Rinko hates it when people turn off the power without saving, right? Not anymore.
Why don't you say, "I won't do it again, please forgive me? Then I'll forgive you.
Say, "I won't do it, please forgive me." Otherwise, Rinko's anger won't subside.
Look Rinko in the eye and say, "I won't do it again, please forgive me? And then I'll forgive you.
Can't you just say, "I won't do it again, please forgive me? It's easy.
"I won't do it again, please forgive me"? It's easy. Come on, say it.
Didn't you hear me? I want you to say, "I won't do it again, please forgive me.
I didn't hear that. Start over.
What? You didn't say that one. Try again.
I can't get through to you then. One more time, please.
That's not fair. Well that's forgivable.
What was that? All right, all right. I forgive you.
Damn. If you do that, I'll have to forgive you, you idiot.
You really told me that? Yeah, I forgive you.
You can say it right. Keep that feeling in mind.
Yeah, of course I forgive you. Heh.
But you can't ever do that again, okay? Promise.
Don't get carried away just because I forgive you. This still hurts, you know.
Please don't do that again, okay? That's the promise you made to Rinko.
Does that mean you I don't have to forgive you?
Don't turn it off without saving it. Don't you ever learn?
I said that's enough! "Don't turn it off without saving it." Huh.
Turning off the power without saving it, if there's something wrong with you, just say it clearly, which is sad.
I don't know what to do. Say, "I love Rinko the most."
If you want me to forgive you, say with all sincerity, "I love Rinko the most!"
If you want me to forgive you, you have to say "I love Rinko the most". You'll tell me, won't you?
Look, you're not gonna tell me?
It's not going to be quiet forever, is it?
Huh? What did you say? I can't hear you.
I can't believe you're faking it like that....
Do you really think that's going to work on Rinko?
I don't want to say that much.
Well it's okay, I heard you correctly.
You're not lying to me, are you? Do you believe Rinko?
Next you can say "I love you" three times. You can say it, right?
But not yet. Next time you have to say "I love you" three times!
Say "I love you" three times, can I trust you?
Already, I wonder why that happens.
It's not like that you know that, don't you?
Yeah that's what I wanted to hear.
I'm so glad you told me. I'm glad you said so.
Promise me this time. No one is going to erase our memories. Get it?
Have you thought about it? Even Rinko doesn't really want to do this, so please don't do it again.
Why don't we make up? You really can't do this anymore. I want to cherish every moment we have together.
Your attitude, is that what you want?
Is that really a reflection on you? Say a bunch of love words to Rinko as punishment.
I think "I'm in love" is the best word to say.
Well you can say "small kick" then. Don't worry about what it means.
See, I'm going to make a sound from my stomach.
Okay! Love I got it right.
You're good! You're setting a record!
I don't feel like I'm feeling sorry for myself. At times like this, you should write a clear reflection.
Yeah, I'll admit that I'm sorry for what I did.
Heh! I've set a new record.
Are you really sorry for what you've done? If you're remorseful, look at Rinko's eyes. If you look away or move, you're out.
You know. You just have to look at Rinko for now.
Heh heh, you should always take this seriously.
New record! I can still stare at it, though?
Just give it up. You should really think about that.
Well I'll leave it at that for now.
